      "name": "Monte Carlo UQ validation — five operating points",
      "description": "Monte Carlo sampling over inlet boundary conditions and blood viscosity parameters was performed across all five flow-speed combinations. 1000 samples per operating point; 95th-percentile hemolysis index reported with structured uncertainty bounds.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/mc-hemolysis-vad-5op"
    },
    {
